síntesis pared","guid":"bfqdg2yzvpltM8LUGKwwAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"- Inhibición\\Nsíntesis proteica","guid":"BQXgZnjnu1VZHFwmIV95_A","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"- Aminoglucósidos: unión ribosoma, inhiben síntesis proteica","guid":"LTaAYXckAGxB293aY4H4-g","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"- Macrólidos: unión subunidad 50S ribosoma","guid":"aK7Rv0bSWrtpIreoSqlIxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"13","text":"- Inhibición síntesis ácidos nucleicos (fluoroquinolonas y sulfas)","guid":"QaXwSzWCkmdYcLt6ZIQ6hg","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"- Fluoroquinolonas: inhiben topoisomerasas, síntesis ADN","guid":"ZPVC10fGZ55GvGFZO1MZRQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"1","text":"Desarrollo de\\Nresistencia","guid":"N7ImUGpp6VZiFCDrFoouew","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"General","guid":"","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Uso excesivo e indiscriminado → aparición y ↑↑ de resistencias","guid":"MKIz-xhlUdZpNpW7XgzjKw","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"↗️ consumo ATM en países de altos ingresos","guid":"EHy0-UE0LUh40Gb0XsuUBw","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"Resistencia = problema de salud pública global","guid":"R2XF2wedaLIwtmeXB2RYUA","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"22","text":"Clave: uso racional y responsable","guid":"fwDgNA34bZxfsEtCOkbyrw","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"21","text":"Mecanismos: mutaciones genéticas,\\Nplásmidos, transposones","guid":"bh6OIGGXNahldo4PITwuBw","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Mecanismos","guid":"V7DwUCCoPr8awq0QHKzcgA","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"- Producción β-lactamasas","guid":"NQSf4TZeNzAWeTSROgqARw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"- Alteración dianas moleculares","guid":"L0XyhW-VkLdbafpDcOvi0Q","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"- Bombas de eflujo","guid":"JRgjHzPatb1VcB1XExLAog","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"27","text":"Resistencias\\Nintrínsecas","guid":"II50VkKj4CsrvvCkTcT0uA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"- Enterococos: resistencia penicilina, vancomicina","guid":"Ocfgl22azn8xRu2yInayVg","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"- S. aureus: resistencia meticilina, producción β-lactamasas","guid":"NG0pOhpppVttH_saGWJsEQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"1","text":"Consumo de\\Nantimicrobianos","guid":"Q5sv02ljZHJA16cgNX9neg","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Medición en Dosis Diarias Definidas (DDD)","guid":"e93npyB8WplLJPPDIs9-7w","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"DDD = dosis promedio diaria para uso principal en adultos","guid":"WgWNakjudjseBet9EbsIig","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"Permite comparar consumo entre países","guid":"Q49rvylvZQkTnCnTdDGfug","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"Problema: baja generación de nuevos ATM\\N(poco rentable vs. fármacos crónicos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"35","text":"OMS promueve políticas para ↗️ I+D de nuevos ATM","guid":"QdS233zSv45SPoLmL_NFAA","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"35","text":"Resistencia aparece a los pocos meses de introducir nuevo ATM","guid":"Xmn1Nje1EPVRL3MHbuaqMA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"0","text":"Principios de\\Nuso de ATM","guid":"TtvlAX1gXGQL_Z7yGalFNg","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"1. Usar ATB cuando hay sospecha\\Nde infección bacteriana","guid":"JIONkhyakENyA8ioTPt83Q","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"• Muchas infecciones virales o enfermedades no infecciosas simulan los signos y sintomas de una infección bacteriana","guid":"LQMntz1fXaEcIO5CCyDnKA","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"• No subestimar los riesgos del uso de ATB -> 20%","guid":"f79jLVBVHFAgsJOgPXv_Uw","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"• No tomar cultivos (+) como sinónimo de infección","guid":"cNfN7m0aUt0qMGVqXug1rw","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"colonización, contaminación","guid":"RizLNTLkAQZ6n52PTIUGxQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"43","text":"• Tomar en cuenta cultivos de sitios no estériles","guid":"KsyryjSukp47TX2BSLc_3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"42","text":"2. Aún cuando sea una infección bacteriana\\Ntratar sólo si cambiará el curso clínico","guid":"SQeCXGfY4WZkjrlleQSjoQ","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• La administración de un ATB no debe ser un acto reflejo a una infección —> debe estar involucrado en un plan terapéutico del paciente","guid":"eqHn3xrYUHgyEDleJUPLsQ","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"• Ejemplos:","guid":"K0Dn7H1rzlh0aT0WWEQPow","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"osteomielitis crónica, tto. en paciente terminal","guid":"5GXqCJD5U2sgCKsR-xOpDQ","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"TARV en un paciente que no será adherente","guid":"YN9HqQQVimx4Bo56UbcVlw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"42","text":"3. Tratamiento\\Nempírico adecuado","guid":"VRr06is-6NYD4a9Ef-egtA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• Amplio para cubrir los posibles MO dentro del Dg diferencial","guid":"X-17dD8vLMVInuCUKPT90Q","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"• Infecciones nosocomiales\\Nusualmente por MO mas resistentes","guid":"SAXqclQJ2tBG7cG7c0bSXg","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"SAMR, Pseudomonas u otros","guid":"S-EqKi7v2MxGy2RJLMBx0w","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"BGN no fermentadores","guid":"MwVjOD7R8sN-d4drJDVAgQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"54","text":"• Infecciones comunitarias → no necesitamos cubrir rutinariamente estos MO MDR","guid":"YQjmpy8W0rFbkekANiPbkg","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"• Muy importante la epidemiologia local","guid":"K9f21AUx1j9nVMk-c93hRg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"42","text":"4. Bajo umbral para inicio de\\NATB en pacientes críticos","guid":"CHIhwAeapzZYLSusNEoYlA","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Paciente HDN estable que consulta por fiebre y CEG → da tiempo para completar estudio sin iniciar ATB empírico","guid":"aZmJyzKvlaU28i9aNXqz9g","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"• Paciente critico en UCI con hipotensión y requerimientos de DVA  → no puede esperar","guid":"YZ9ucX29k6NiOyXJFKTRqg","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"• Paciente crítico → espectro puede ser mas amplio pero cubriendo los MO probables","guid":"D8l_5hRr-ytTvEifah87bQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"• IMPORTANTE ","guid":"DMx9dT-B9OooJ_naZgguhQ","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"→ lo inmediato no debe ser sólo la orden de administrar el ATB, sino también el inicio de la infusión","guid":"QfxDI0eruBcM2L2lI5uxlQ","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"→ si ordenamos múltiples ATB indicar el orden o la forma en que lo administraremos","guid":"RWlLum8T4284QIM_AfjSIA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"42","text":"5. Los factores del huésped afectan la selección del tto,\\Nempírico por que modifican los MO posibles","guid":"T8aQo3EalWofkT8tX5AQiQ","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"• Inmunosuprimid@s","guid":"BYaQlnNNh81Jr0v3eWYkBQ","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"Ampliar el Dg diferencial de MO posibles","guid":"fRVMs24RvmAL6Hx-BYducw","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"• Considerar bacterias atípicas (ej: Listeria, Nocardia), virus, hongos, parásitos","guid":"daxll2QVqCo50YcIAnjjDA","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"68","text":"• Depende del tipo de\\Ninmunosupresión:","guid":"I5edFWH5gOJogRGREVwc-Q","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"• Neutropénicos → bacterianas y posteriormente fúngicas","guid":"cUYuYXk6mk5ouiaoM0JxhA","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"VIH → P. jirovecii, CMV, Toxoplasmosis","guid":"QOZSZXWS5E5W3iMZBk-eHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"68","text":"• TOS/TPH","guid":"ZKbHvQ8eplgISHA_NG1YYA","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"68","text":"• NO es cierto que por tener IS tenga > riesgo de MO MDR","guid":"ADk7wyfZr20T_WjqBb_MWQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"42","text":"6. Principios PK-PD pueden\\Nafectar el tratamiento óptimo","guid":"OY76SyxkzXYkF88VKtUorA","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"• Considerar sitio de infección → bacteriemia, SNC, hueso","guid":"Gyc3Ol2stOF_JfBeGDyD7Q","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"• Considerar que el ATB mantenga el efecto en el sitio de infección","guid":"byQVB1eVeWhD47vlEruyHA","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"42","text":"7. Desescalar según cultivos y\\Nevolución clínica y de laboratorio","guid":"HPd39i92YxNKDWu-OB6vMA","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"• Según MO aislado → gram → cultivo definitivo","guid":"JZ9nxQzR9b1eF5owZoW6Kg","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"• Cuando los cultivos son (-) → foco pulmonar; abdominal, piel y PB → evaluar respuesta clínica y de laboratorio","guid":"AmTaCzT1vUps1VhKZwuhyA","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"42","text":"8. Si la terapia no está funcionando evaluar defocación y diagnósticos alternativos\\N→ antes de pensar en (R) y escalar tratamiento","guid":"RbSe5l4wH_NWIZAcf0OZMQ","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"• Evaluar respuesta a las 48-72 hrs\\N→ ¿no vamos bien?:","guid":"BwtU7wgwXA4Wug9ZCXAu-g","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Control de foco → remover pus y material foráneo","guid":"PSYZWAOPZ6Nwe9DDATp8-g","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"Reconsiderar Dg diferencial → causas no infecciosas, otros MO no bacterianos","guid":"eK0wLAv0yuxFiBxgFaSoIw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"42","text":"9. Distinguir nueva\\Ninfección de falla a tto. Inicial","guid":"O2st_w-ViB5Nw1dTSI5F8w","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"• Si hay respuesta inicial al tto. y existe una reagudización con empeoramiento clínico y de laboratorio\\N→  pensar en una nueva infección","guid":"DD2v7zu8NTZwcIs1UfJO1Q","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"• Menos probable emergencia de resistencia en MO inicialmente tratado","guid":"QMt6g3tOqeRUtZfBR9bPcg","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"42","text":"10. Duración de ATB: basado en evidencia y cursos cortos de ser posible","guid":"bv8OvUHCzzBB35xFZ6w-6g","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"• Cortos → = efectividad, < efectos adversos, < impacto sobre microbioma","guid":"A38F8mtvpxpRRv5tQKUfSg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación","guid":"SrN2pAFX9hMsQjMbTYQnYQ","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"Betalactámicos: amplio\\Nespectro y seguros","guid":"eOk-PUn_2ftNsj43QE8EGA","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"Penicilinas","guid":"erO1MmFI_9t0fwfYONJTXw","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"Cefalosporinas","guid":"nl6COCApZYepuaR_dsIfMg","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"Resistencia natural","guid":"","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Enterococos y L. monocytogenes resistentes a todas las cefalosporinas","guid":"lvTraLg-es-DuQhSRAjg2Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"Cefalosporinas parenterales\\Nde 1.ª generación","guid":"w6DJTQUhQHJnTpL7rYD5Ww","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"Cefazolina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"Uso: Profilaxis en cirugía, infecciones por S. aureus y estreptococos","guid":"EO4rR40jTpifyLJhu4HqBw","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"Inactiva: Staphylococcus coagulasa negativos","guid":"MxFTTJfRe2lDGLaVvWvlaQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"95","text":"Cefalosporinas orales\\Nde 1.ª generación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"Cefradina, cefalexina,\\Ncefadroxilo","guid":"YrfL23jyNfmVmbgEO2ZKpg","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"Actividad: S. aureus, estreptococos, algunos bacilos entéricos","guid":"9xKLFB8vr81HpUd63FVjfg","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"Uso: Infecciones extrahospitalarias","guid":"jXPdpeLDft-1hioObXKbjA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"95","text":"Cefalosporinas orales\\Nde 2.ª generación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"Cefaclor, cefprozilo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"Ineficaces: Infecciones por S. pneumoniae","guid":"d11aKdOHekL1IzfrNCTIxg","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"107","text":"Menor acción: H. influenzae, M. catarrhalis","guid":"LLlsjA8SENZq3qnTpD96eQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"95","text":"Cefalosporinas de 2.ª\\Ngeneración amplio espectro","guid":"","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"Cefamandol, cefuroxima","guid":"","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"Activo: S. pneumoniae, H.\\Ninfluenzae, M. catarrhalis, E.\\Ncoli, N. gonorrhoeae","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"95","text":"Cefalosporinas de\\N3.ª generación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"Cefotaxima, ceftriaxona","guid":"SEOjBPbxGpltp31N-1MOnA","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"Mayor actividad: S. pneumoniae, H. influenzae, N. meningitidis","guid":"z9byOXs-Og6v6MznM-13ZQ","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"Inactivas: P. aeruginosa, cepas productoras de BLEE y AmpC","guid":"wd-9kdqnYkEs1cGPfOl1Bw","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"113","text":"Ceftazidima, cefoperazona","guid":"MfTDlGgWEBrA5tjF_iCd6Q","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"Actividad: P. aeruginosa","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"113","text":"Cefepime (4.ª generación)","guid":"6i6kNBJgapv7U_9oY2jNZw","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"Alta actividad: P. aeruginosa, bacilos entéricos productores de AmpC","guid":"owy66YBtZNDCQl4b5GpI6g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"95","text":"Cefalosporinas de\\N5.ª generación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"Ceftarolina, ceftobiprol","guid":"","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"Activas: SARM, S. pneumoniae resistente a penicil